/*!
\page handle_glshow GLSHOW Show a GL Assembly in a GL Window

<p>
Section: \ref sec_handle "Handle-Based Graphics"
\section Usage
Shows a GL Assembly in a GL Window.  The syntax for its
use is
\verbatim
  glshow(name,scale)
\endverbatim
which shows the <tt>glassembly</tt> named <tt>name</tt> in a new GL
window, with the scale set to <tt>scale</tt>.  Roughly speaking
<tt>scale</tt> should represent the radial size of the object
that you want to see in the window.
*/
